item.title: CVE-2022-28766|2024-09-16T22:31:26.358Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20client%20for%20meetings%20for%20windows%20%2832-bit%29
item.description: Windows 32-bit versions of the Zoom Client for Meetings before 5.12.6 and Zoom Rooms for Conference Room before version 5.12.6 are susceptible to a DLL injection vulnerability. A local low-privileged user could exploit this vulnerability to run arbitrary code in the context of the Zoom client.
